Zyzzyva is free software, released under the GNU General Public License.
Please see COPYING and LICENSE for details.

To build Zyzzyva, you will need the Qt4 library, available from
http://www.trolltech.com/download/opensource.html.

After Qt4 is installed, the following steps should be sufficient to
build Zyzzyva:

    qmake
    make

The Zyzzyva home page is http://zyzzyva.net/, and the latest version can
always be found there.  Please email Michael W Thelen <mthelen@gmail.com>
with questions, comments, patches, or large cash donations.  Happy hacking!
